title: Leafy Green
description: A head of a rich green leaf vegetable, usually shown with white stalks. May be used to represent a variety of greens, including romaine lettuce, chard, and Chinese cabbage like bok choy, as commonly cooked in Asian cuisines.
apple_vendor_description: The leafy green emoji on Apple devices showcases a single, fresh, and slightly dewy leaf with a beautiful gradient of emerald and forest green.  Its smooth, rounded edges and subtle highlights suggest vitality and natural growth, embodying the essence of nature and health.  This emoji is commonly used on Apple devices to represent healthy eating, environmental awareness, or simply the beauty of the outdoors.
